item.title: Team Meeting Thursday, July 26 at 7:00pm
item.description: We have a team meeting on Thursday evening, July 26, at Derek's house. This will be in place of our regular Thursday evening recreational playing. The purpose is to plan for the Fall, including, but not limited to, the Fall league season.

item.title: Spring League Registration

item.title: USTA Spring Men's 3.5 Roster Grid
item.description: The intial Roster Grid for Adult Men's 3.5 USTA Spring League is up. Please go to it, login, and record your availability for the season.
